               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Fǝtḥa nagaśt “Justice of the Kings” (fols. 4ra-228rb) 
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 4ra-10rb) 
 - Table of contents (fols. 10rb-11rb) 
                     - Ecclesiastical laws (fols. 11rb-102ra) 
 - Civil laws (fols. 102rb-223vb)
                     
 - Law of Patriarch Cyril concerning land transaction (fols.
                     223vb-228rb)
 
 Additiones 1-3; colophon.</summary>
