                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#2ra">ff. 2ra-3</locus>
                           <desc>vb, 229ra-232rb: Fäws Manfasawi “Spiritual Medicine”, unidentified
                              canon law text.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> Written in a secondary hand, in bleak ink. The text contains
                              penitentiary regulations; in the explicit, it is called Śǝrʿāta qänona
                              "Canonical rules". </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus from="229ra11" to="229ra15">f. 229ra, l.11-15</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#229ra">229ra</locus>, l.11: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘመምህር፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡
                              ዘአጥረዮ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ይኩኖ፡ ለመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮ[sic]፡
                              ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note states that the Ms. was in the possession of Kidāna
                              Māryām. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#229vb">ff. 229vb-230</locus>
                           <desc>rb: Rules concerning the schedule of the celebration of the
                              Mass.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> Crudely written in a secondary hand; partly faded. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title of the work ፍትሃ፡ ነገስት is crudely written on
                           the front board in large felt-tip pen.
 - Seal of the parish council
                           of Golʿa Dabra Bǝrhān Yoḥannǝs church: <locus target="#4r">4r</locus>,
                           116r, 232r.
 - Crude note written in pen in the upper margin: <locus target="#81v">81v</locus>.
 - Corrections over erasures on many
                           fols., carefully executed in the main hand: e.g., <locus target="#8v">8v</locus>, 9r, 14ra, 14v, 15r etc.
 - Corrected passages are
                           written over erasures interlineally, in somewhat smaller script, in the
                           same hand, on many fols.: e.g., <locus target="#11ra">11ra</locus>, 13va,
                           18va, 38ra etc.
 - Erasures marked with thin black and red lines, on
                           many fols.: e.g., <locus target="#12va">12va-</locus>vb, 13va, 20ra, 24vb
                           etc.
 - Omitted letter or word added interlineally: <locus target="#14vb">14vb</locus>.
 - Omitted passage added in the upper
                           margin (?): <locus target="#32r">32r</locus>.
 - A sign in the shape
                           of cross (possibly tamallas-sign, but no omitted text passages are
                           indicated in the margin), poorly visible, on many fols.: e.g., <locus target="#31v">31v</locus>, 34v, 36r, 40r, 45r, 49v etc.
 -
                           Tamallas-sign in the shapf of two perpendicular lines, indicating where
                           the omitted word or letters, written in the margin in a secondary hand,
                           belong: <locus target="#41v">41v</locus>, 43r(?), 47v, 50r, 52r,
                           53r.
 - A passage of the text is taken in a red frame: <locus target="#45v">45v</locus>.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- Rubricated notes written in the upper margin refer
                              to the content of the sections: በእንተ፡ ጾመ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ: <locus target="#23v">fol. 23v</locus>. በእንተ፡ ከመ፡ ይትመጦ፡ ቍርባነ: <locus target="#24r">fol. 24r</locus>. በእንተ፡ ነገረ፡ ጉባኤ: <locus target="#31v">fol. 31v</locus>. - A thread is inserted on the outer
                              edge of fols. 31, 71, 78, 109, 120, 219.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">Shelfmark 8, 24/8/93 (fol 1r)</item>
                     </list>
